* :aname.Buelens Kris                    :anode.BEVM :auser.BUELENSC
* :support.NA           :doc.Built-in help    :lang.REXX, XEDIT
* :sw.VM/SP R5 & up or VM/ESA, DIRMAP (of CMS Utilities feature)
* :abs.This package provides a simple interface to manage the CP directory
*    - Helps with finding free space for new minidisks (automatic or manual)
*    - Checks for overlaps before placing the directory online
*    - Can be used to see only users with certain options
*    - Helps to defragment disks (DIRMAINT and/or DFSMS is required then)
*    In general: a poor man's DIRMAINT alternative
*    If you have DIRMAINT: enhances DIRMAINT a little bit,
*    If you have RACFVM: makes it easier to enter RACF commands
