* Tailoring:
*  1.  Major defintions: Xedit the DRM NAMESAMP and file into DRM NAMES
*  2.  Your XEDIT settings: PROFDRM XEDIT
*  3.  Create "GAPFILE VOLSERS" if not all disks available for CMS       mdisk
*                   (type HELP DRM or HELP DIRMAP for more info)
*  4.  If using RACF, tailor the skeletons: RACFDRM SKEL*                TXA'
      DRMAC    EXEC     *   LINK to directory mdisks & start DRM
      DRM      EXEC     *   Xedit the Directory if you have the LINKs
